properties.note: TIGER Roads 2018 data lists the name of this as "Meyer Drive," however, UCSC has assigned McHenry Library's address as "414 McHenry Road," so McHenry Road e seems to be "more locally, authoritatively defined."

After manually walking the length of this path I dont believe track is the correct classification as there is really only enough room for walking. At one point I believe a two track vehicle drove over this while it was muddy which is why it looks this way
At this point heading north, this way becomes indistinguishable between the path and the adjacent gutter, but south of this point it is only a drainage gutter.
